                    "line_text": "Je trouvai deux enfants couchés au pied d'un houx,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Deux enfants qui jouaient, sur le sable, aux cailloux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et soudain, dans mon cœur cette vie innocente,",
